Use Math.floor and ensure all drawing is in integers
use one of these - can avoid adding 0.5 if we want?
// With a bitwise or.
rounded = (0.5 + somenum) | 0;
// A double bitwise not.
rounded = ~~ (0.5 + somenum);
// Finally, a left bitwise shift.
rounded = (0.5 + somenum) << 0;

